<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= title %></title>
    <style>
        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0a0a0a 0%, #1a1a2e 100%);
            color: #e0e0e0;
            min-height: 100vh;
            padding: 40px 20px;
        }
        .container { max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            padding: 40px;
            background: linear-gradient(160deg, #111, #1a1a2e);
            border-radius: 16px;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 195, 0, 0.2);
            box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
        }
        .logo {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 12px;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
        }
        .logo-mark {
            width: 48px; height: 48px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ffc300, #ff9900);
            border-radius: 12px;
            display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
            font-weight: 800; font-size: 18px; color: #000;
        }
        .logo-text { font-size: 28px; font-weight: 700; color: #ffc300; }
        h1 { font-size: 24px; color: #fff; margin-bottom: 8px; }
        .subtitle { color: #888; font-size: 14px; }
        .badge {
            display: inline-block;
            background: rgba(255, 195, 0, 0.15);
            color: #ffc300;
            padding: 4px 16px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 13px;
            margin-top: 12px;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 195, 0, 0.3);
        }
        .stats-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
            gap: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }
        .stat-card {
            background: linear-gradient(160deg, #111, #0d0d0d);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 195, 0, 0.15);
            border-radius: 16px;
            padding: 28px;
            text-align: center;
            transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
        }
        .stat-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-4px);
            box-shadow: 0 12px 24px rgba(255, 195, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .stat-value {
            font-size: 42px;
            font-weight: 800;
            color: #ffc300;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }
        .stat-label { color: #888; font-size: 14px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1px; }
        .card {
            background: linear-gradient(160deg, #111, #0d0d0d);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 195, 0, 0.15);
            border-radius: 16px;
            padding: 28px;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
        }
        .card h2 {
            font-size: 20px;
            color: #ffc300;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
        }
        table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; }
        th {
            text-align: left;
            padding: 12px 16px;
            color: #888;
            font-size: 13px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            border-bottom: 2px solid rgba(255, 195, 0, 0.2);
        }
        td {
            padding: 14px 16px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        .status-badge {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 4px 12px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-transform: capitalize;
        }
        .status-new { background: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.15); color: #3b82f6; }
        .status-approved { background: rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.15); color: #10b981; }
        .status-assigned { background: rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.15); color: #8b5cf6; }
        .status-completed { background: rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.15); color: #22c55e; }
        .status-cancelled { background: rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.15); color: #ef4444; }
        .empty-state {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 40px;
            color: #555;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 30px;
            color: #555;
            font-size: 13px;
            border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
            margin-top: 40px;
        }
        .tech-stack {
            display: flex;
            gap: 8px;
            justify-content: center;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            margin-top: 12px;
        }
        .tech-tag {
            background: rgba(255, 195, 0, 0.1);
            color: #ffc300;
            padding: 4px 12px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            font-size: 11px;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 195, 0, 0.2);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <!-- Header -->
        <div class="header">
            <div class="logo">
                <div class="logo-mark">UC</div>
                <span class="logo-text">UrbanCrew</span>
            </div>
            <h1>Server-Side Rendered Dashboard</h1>
            <p class="subtitle">This page is rendered using EJS Template Engine on the server</p>
            <span class="badge">🕐 Server Time: <%= serverTime %></span>
        </div>

        <!-- Stats -->
        <div class="stats-grid">
            <div class="stat-card">
                <div class="stat-value"><%= stats.totalUsers %></div>
                <div class="stat-label">Total Users</div>
            </div>
            <div class="stat-card">
                <div class="stat-value"><%= stats.totalRequests %></div>
                <div class="stat-label">Total Requests</div>
            </div>
            <div class="stat-card">
                <div class="stat-value"><%= stats.totalWorkers %></div>
                <div class="stat-label">Total Workers</div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Recent Requests -->
        <div class="card">
            <h2>📋 Recent Requests</h2>
            <% if (recentRequests.length > 0) { %>
                <table>
                    <thead>
                        <tr>
                            <th>Service Type</th>
                            <th>Workers</th>
                            <th>Location</th>
                            <th>Duration</th>
                            <th>Status</th>
                        </tr>
                    </thead>
                    <tbody>
                        <% recentRequests.forEach(function(request) { %>
                            <tr>
                                <td style="text-transform: capitalize;"><%= request.serviceType %></td>
                                <td><%= request.numberOfWorkers %></td>
                                <td><%= request.location %></td>
                                <td style="text-transform: capitalize;"><%= request.duration %></td>
                                <td>
                                    <span class="status-badge status-<%= request.status %>">
                                        <%= request.status %>
                                    </span>
                                </td>
                            </tr>
                        <% }); %>
                    </tbody>
                </table>
            <% } else { %>
                <div class="empty-state">
                    <p>No requests found yet. Create some from the React dashboard!</p>
                </div>
            <% } %>
        </div>

        <!-- Technology Info -->
        <div class="card">
            <h2>⚙️ Technology Stack</h2>
            <p style="color: #888; margin-bottom: 16px; line-height: 1.8;">
                This UrbanCrew backend is built with a modern Node.js stack demonstrating
                key concepts from the BEE syllabus including client-server architecture,
                RESTful APIs, middleware, authentication, and template engines.
            </p>
            <div class="tech-stack">
                <span class="tech-tag">Node.js</span>
                <span class="tech-tag">Express.js</span>
                <span class="tech-tag">MongoDB Atlas</span>
                <span class="tech-tag">Mongoose</span>
                <span class="tech-tag">JWT</span>
                <span class="tech-tag">bcrypt</span>
                <span class="tech-tag">Socket.io</span>
                <span class="tech-tag">EJS</span>
                <span class="tech-tag">Sessions</span>
                <span class="tech-tag">Cookies</span>
                <span class="tech-tag">REST API</span>
                <span class="tech-tag">Middleware</span>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Footer -->
        <div class="footer">
            <p>UrbanCrew © 2024 — BEE Project | Server-Side Rendered with EJS</p>
            <p style="margin-top: 8px;">
                Rendered at: <strong><%= serverTime %></strong> (IST)
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
